text.value: Keep up to date with the latest improvements in ToolJet!

schema.value:
{{queries.1dd176cc-6809-4c66-8772-f3e7de9a4fb8.data
    .filter(note => components.d27d3b60-6fd9-4892-b978-597e45272f9f.value || !!note.lts_release_tag)
    .sort((a, b) => a.tag.localeCompare(b.tag))
    .filter((option, index, self) => index === self.findIndex((t) => t.tag === option.tag))
    .map(option => ({
        label: option.tag,
        value: option.tag,
        disable: false,
        visible: true,
        default: option.tag === 'v3.0.1-ee-lts' 
    }))}}
